 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Blaze:

    When this Pokémon has 1/3 or 
  less of its HP remaining, its 
  fire-type moves inflict 1.5× 
  as much regular damage.

  Solar-power:

    During strong sunlight, this 
  Pokémon has 1.5× its Special 
  Attack but takes 1/8 of its maximum 
  HP in damage after each turn.


